name: RaspLAMP Server Homepage
tagline: WAMP Server's Homepage - Remade for Linux (specifically Raspberry Pi + LAMP Setup)
body:
### Welcome to RaspLAMP Server Homepage.
This repository hosts a Linux compatible modification of WAMP Server's GPL Licensed "index.php" file which was made for Windows OS'.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
